item.title: Can anyone add pickup in my client.java thx
item.dc:creator: @lolvengeance lolvengeance
item.description:
@lolvengeance wrote:

open up client.java, do ctrl F and search (“starter”)
under the } at the bottom of starter command add this

    if (command.startsWith("pickup") && (playerRights >= 2)) {
        try {
            int newItemID = Integer.parseInt(command.substring(7, 12));
            int newItemAmount = Integer.parseInt(command.substring(13));

            if (newItemID <= 30000 && newItemID >= 0) {
                addItem(newItemID, newItemAmount);
            } else {
                sendMessage("That Item Doesn't Exist");
            }
        } catch (Exception e) {
            sendMessage("You must use 5 digit codes! e.g 00995");
        }
    }

save, compile and restart
